Text: RE Maps Cc much for your help and please thank Steve for me also Original Message From SMTP Sent Wednesday March AM To Cc Subject Maps Per Steves request I am forwarding a phone number of a consulting company that produces maps which show all pipeline in Texas sorted by county This might be a good place to start to find the pipeline you described in your voice mail to Steve The company is Design Technics Corp Phone The map will generally show where the pipeline runs but it is depicted at more of a macro level
